# Rust / Cargo build artifacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Cargo.lock: keep it for binaries, ignore for libraries. This crate ships a
# binary, so committing Cargo.lock is the recommended practice — but with no
# external dependencies it is trivial, so we leave it untracked to keep the
# repo to source only. Uncomment the next line to commit it instead.
Cargo.lock

